When I started Quasar , I am telling you working with such new thin intense textures was a new thing for me. I was surprised when my cam wasn’t able to pick on the beautiful shift which was however visible to me off camera. Displaying it was a major need and I was not doing justice to it. 

It had been a new journey for me to find right tools, light setups (different from anything I had done in the past) . Almost 6 months later , I am able to do justice to them. So proud of this thing today, this wasn’t easy for me 

Will share a few tips and tricks soon that I observed about lights and their types. ✨

On my lips - MULTICHROME - QUASAR 
This was the very first shade we dropped in the store. Will always be special. ♥️

#multichrome #iseequasar #multichromeeyeshadow

latestPosts.caption:
COSMIC CRUSH - close up swatches 🪄

Quasar is welcoming a new series of pigments which are SMART chrome textures, these not only have massive bling , a spectacular shift but also change their core color over dark bases as shown in the video! 

With just one pigment you can either have light coloured looks or you can alter its color pairing it with a darker base. The possibilities are endless with this series. 

Cosmic Crush by Quasar is a mid point of all the pigment series combined together and offers the best of our multiverse. 

The shade names are -
Vulcan 
Celina 
Zenith 
Aster 

#iseequasar #multichrome #multichromeeyeshadow #multichromemakeup

Dear brands, unpaid work kills creativity and art.

As an artist and creator I am open to showcase any gifted product in my reels and I freely talk about those in my stories but curating dedicated media for commercial purposes is not something I would wanna do, it isn’t giving ! 

At the same time , I am extremely grateful to the brands who have valued working with me from such a long time and trusting me with what I produce for them.
